attributes.review: This app is absolutely pitiful! I wanted to see what this orange Cheeto puff with a croissant on its head was up to. Once I download it and entered my mobile number, I got a text demanding a ransom! They wanted to hold my pig, Peppa, hostage! I quickly ran to check if she was there, and she wasn’t. I then saw a fighter jet leaving the premises. It was decorated with “All hail Trump.”  There was a tight sensation on my chest, and my anxiety began to increase. I had a heart attack. Luckily my frog, Pepe, was able to save me. If I could rate this -273.15° C I would! An app has never introduced so much pain into my life. I don’t think I could ever recover from this 😣
attributes.title: Held Peppa Hostage
